OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to four-year-old
OL,4,Cboy who died following house fire
OL,6,FThe family of a four-year-old boy who
OL,7,Fdied following a house fire which also
OL,8,Fclaimed the life of his father said he
OL,9,F'didn't want his daddy to be alone'.
OL,11,FEthan Mason, aged four, had been in an
OL,12,Finduced coma after the fire at his
OL,13,Fhome on Warrington Road, , in the
OL,14,Fearly hours of 14 April, 2024.
OL,16,FWitnesses said his dad Barry, 45, ran
OL,17,Fback into the house to save his son.
OL,19,FEthan died in hospital on 17 April,
OL,20,F2024.
