OL,6,FEthan's aunt, Jessica, paid tribute to
OL,7,Fhim on her Facebook page: "Little
OL,8,FEthan decided he didn't want his daddy
OL,9,Fto be alone, and he is now back in his
OL,10,Farms.
OL,12,F"As a family we are all completely
OL,13,Fbroken but want to thank you, every
OL,14,Fsingle one of you, for your words of
OL,15,Flove and support."JTo help support the
OL,16,Ffamily following the tragedy, a has
OL,17,Fbeen set up.
