OL,6,FBouquets of flowers, handwritten
OL,7,Ftributes and a child's Spiderman
OL,8,Fcushion have been laid outside the
OL,9,Fhome. Nearby residents are
OL,10,F'devastated' by the tragic incident.
OL,12,F"There's been a huge wave of sadness,"
OL,13,Fsaid one woman, who lives with her
OL,14,Ffamily along Warrington Road.
OL,16,F"People can say what they want about
OL,17,Fthis place, but the community comes
OL,18,Ftogether.J"They're a beautiful family.
OL,19,FIt must be so horrific what they're
OL,20,Fgoing through."
