OL,6,Fdo not believe that there are any
OL,7,Fsuspicious circumstances surrounding
OL,8,Fincident. are investigating the causes
OL,9,Fof the fire and are working with the
OL,10,Fpolice.JDetective Inspector Lee
OL,11,FGridley, from GMP's Wigan district,
OL,12,Fsaid: "This is a devastating incident
OL,13,Fand all of our thoughts are with the
OL,14,Ffamily of this young boy, who had his
OL,15,Fentire life ahead of him.J"Together
OL,16,Fwith the earlier death, this is a
OL,17,Ftragedy for the Wigan community and I
OL,18,Fknow that many people will be shocked
OL,19,Fby this heartbreaking news.
