OL,6,F"I hope people will join us in sending
OL,7,Ftheir absolute best wishes to all
OL,8,Fthose involved in this incident, as
OL,9,Fthey begin their journey in the
OL,10,Fhealing process.
OL,12,F"While we are not treating the
OL,13,Fincident as suspicious, if anyone has
OL,14,Fany information they believe is
OL,15,Fimportant, please do get in touch with
OL,16,Fus. You can do this by calling police
OL,17,Fon 101, quoting log 393 of 14/04/2024."
